  card "Session would be\n[c1..c5]" as FULL
}

rectangle "**extensionSessions**" #FFF3E0 {
  card "covered = {c1,c2,c3}\nuncovered = [c4,c5]" as EXT
  card "Write **groups/T5.json**\nextension group only" as OUT
}

DEV --> NC
G1 --> EXT : coveredCommitHashes
FULL --> EXT : subtract covered
EXT --> OUT

note bottom of OUT
  report resume folds **T5** only — no duplicate
  history from re-folding [c1..c5].
  Graph only extends; delete artifacts to rebuild.
end note

@enduml


@startuml commit-group-rerun
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

title **Incremental re-run** (append-only graph)

actor "Developer" as DEV

rectangle "**Re-run after new commits**" #E8F5E9 {
  card "evidence + summarize\nnew commits only" as INC1
  card "commit-group\n**extension groups**\n(uncovered commits)" as INC2
  card "report resume\n+ prepare + final\n**extension mode**" as INC3
}

DEV --> INC1
INC1 --> INC2
INC2 --> INC3

note bottom
  **Incremental:** extension groups + cumulative Q&A in final (§11).
  Existing JSON model layers are never overwritten.
  To rebuild a stage: delete its artifacts manually.
  evidence re-run only needed if Git export changed.
end note

@enduml


@startuml commit-group-sequence
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence — **commit-group** (summarize in, evidence out)

actor "Developer" as DEV
database "commits/*.json\n(D evidence)" as COMM
database "summaries/*.json\n(M:c canonical)" as SUMM
database "project.json" as PJ
participant "**commit-group**" as CG
participant "Ollama\ncommitModel" as LLM
database "groups/<ts>.json" as GRP

DEV -> CG : commit-group ./repo

CG -> COMM : load evidence manifests
CG -> SUMM : join canonical summaries
CG -> CG : filter empty summaries\n(isEmptyCommitSummary)

note over COMM
  evidence .patch files **not read**
  .partN / .merge summaries **not read**
end note

CG -> CG : groupByGap + **extensionSessions**\n(subtract covered commit hashes)

note over CG
  **Incremental re-run:** extension groups
  = uncovered commits only (§4).
  Skips groups with model (append-only).
end note

CG -> CG : buildGroupRecord (D)\naggregateDeterministic\npartitionTiers from commit.model signals

CG -> PJ : loadProjectContext()

CG -> LLM : **Session 1 classify**\nmember summaries + signals + questions
LLM --> CG : session signals, questions[], context tiers

CG -> LLM : **Session 2 compose**\nsummaries by tier + classify result
LLM --> CG : history

CG -> CG : mergeTechnologies (D)\n+ provenance

CG -> GRP : write group JSON

CG --> DEV : summarized / skipped / failed counts

@enduml


